<text><body>
<lb n="0206c07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0206c08"/>
<lb n="0206c09"/><head type="no">No. 1086 [No. 1087]</head>
<lb n="0206c10"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0206070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】高山寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本塚本賢曉氏藏</note>觀自在菩薩如意輪瑜伽<note n="0206071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一卷＝念誦法【明】，〔一卷〕－&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0206071"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">念誦法</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0206c11"/>
<lb n="0206c12"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0206072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…譯）四十六字＝（唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯）十六字【明】【乙】，（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯）二十二字【甲】</note><note n="0206072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…譯）四十六字＝（唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯）十六字【明】【乙】，＝（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯）二十二字【甲】</note><app n="0206072" word-count="46"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0206c13"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0206c14"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0206c15"/>不空奉　詔譯</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0206c16"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>我今順瑜伽</l><l>金剛頂經說</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0207a" n="0207a"/>
<lb n="0207a01"/><l>摩尼蓮花部</l><l>如意念誦法</l>
<lb n="0207a02"/><l>修此三昧故</l><l>能如觀自在</l>
<lb n="0207a03"/><l>先擇其弟子</l><l>族姓敬法者</l>
<lb n="0207a04"/><l>多人所敬愛</l><l>智慧而勇進</l>
<lb n="0207a05"/><l>決定毘離耶</l><l>覺慧常不捨</l>
<lb n="0207a06"/><l>盡孝於父母</l><l>淨信於三寶</l>
<lb n="0207a07"/><l>樂修菩提行</l><l>於四無量心</l>
<lb n="0207a08"/><l>剎那無有間</l><l>常樂大乘法</l>
<lb n="0207a09"/><l>住於菩薩戒</l><l>恭敬阿闍<note n="0207001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梨＝黎【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207001"><lem>梨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">黎</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0207a10"/><l>一切諸聖者</l><l>成就堅固力</l>
<lb n="0207a11"/><l>丈夫之勇猛</l><l>善通相應門</l>
<lb n="0207a12"/><l>常樂寂靜行</l><l>智慧無所畏</l>
<lb n="0207a13"/><l>以戒常嚴身</l><l>精修祕密乘</l>
<lb n="0207a14"/><l>敬依理趣道</l><l>一心無所&CB00385;</l>
<lb n="0207a15"/><l>常樂聞妙法</l><l>曾入三昧耶</l>
<lb n="0207a16"/><l>從師獲灌頂</l><l>既蒙印可已</l>
<lb n="0207a17"/><l>不久當成就</l><l>弟子具此相</l>
<lb n="0207a18"/><l>方可為傳授</l><l>此即如意寶</l>
<lb n="0207a19"/><l>能成諸事業</l><l>如經說處所</l>
<lb n="0207a20"/><l>山間及流水</l><l>清淨阿蘭若</l>
<lb n="0207a21"/><l>隨樂之&CB00589;谷</l><l>離諸<note n="0207002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">危＝厄&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0207002"><lem>危</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">厄</rdg></app>怖難</l>
<lb n="0207a22"/><l>隨力嚴供<note n="0207003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝養【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207003"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">養</rdg></app></l><l>行人面於西</l>
<lb n="0207a23"/><l>漫提自在王</l><l>次禮餘方佛</l>
<lb n="0207a24"/><l>以五輪著地</l><l>如教之敬禮</l>
<lb n="0207a25"/><l>雙膝長跪已</l><l>合掌虛心住</l>
<lb n="0207a26"/><l>誠心盡陳說</l><l>三業一切罪</l>
<lb n="0207a27"/><l>我從過去世</l><l>流轉於生死</l>
<lb n="0207a28"/><l>今對大聖尊</l><l>盡心而懺悔</l>
<lb n="0207a29"/><l>如先佛所懺</l><l>我今亦如是</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0207b" n="0207b"/>
<lb n="0207b01"/><l>願<note n="0207004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">承＝垂【甲】</note><app n="0207004"><lem>承</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">垂</rdg></app>加持力</l><l>眾生悉清淨</l>
<lb n="0207b02"/><l>以此大願故</l><l>自他獲無垢</l></lg>
<lb n="0207b03"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0207b04"/><p type="dharani">唵　薩<note n="0207005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝&CB00085;【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207005"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app>婆　&CB00085;輸馱　薩婆達麼　薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0207b05"/>婆&CB00085;輸度唅</p>
<lb n="0207b06"/><p>行者次應隨喜一切諸佛菩薩所集福智<note place="inline">思一切佛
<lb n="0207b07"/>菩薩過去所修行功德如我自作而生歡喜</note></p>
<lb n="0207b08"/><lg><l>過現三世佛</l><l>菩薩及眾聖</l>
<lb n="0207b09"/><l>所集諸善根</l><l>合掌盡隨喜</l>
<lb n="0207b10"/><l>如我身所集</l><l>歡喜無有異</l></lg>
<lb n="0207b11"/><p>次應右膝著地芙蓉合掌置於頂上。想禮一
<lb n="0207b12"/>切如來菩薩足</p><p type="inline">密言曰</p>
<lb n="0207b13"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;頭麼<note place="inline">二合</note>微<note place="inline">微古<note n="0207006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207006"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0207b14"/><p>禮諸佛已<note n="0207007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">全跏半跏＝全加而坐【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207007"><lem>全跏半跏</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">全加而坐</rdg></app>。或輪王<note n="0207008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跏＝加【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207008"><lem>跏</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">加</rdg></app>。隨<note n="0207009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝喜【甲】</note><app n="0207009"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>而
<lb n="0207b15"/>坐</p>
<lb n="0207b16"/><lg><l>作此坐印已</l><l>觀遍虛空佛</l>
<lb n="0207b17"/><l>己身各於前</l><l>住彼眾聖會</l>
<lb n="0207b18"/><l>止觀從膝上</l><l>旋舞當心合</l>
<lb n="0207b19"/><l>如蓮之未敷</l><l>想禮於諸佛</l>
<lb n="0207b20"/><l>次結三昧耶</l><l>當心堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0207b21"/><l>檀慧禪智&CB00594;</l><l>金剛蓮花印</l>
<lb n="0207b22"/><l>通持蓮花者</l><l>警覺<note n="0207010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＝諸【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207010"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>聖已</l>
<lb n="0207b23"/><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0207b24"/><p type="dharani">唵跋折<note n="0207011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉二合【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207011"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉二合</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note n="0207012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207012"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>三麼耶薩怛梵<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0207b25"/><lg><l>由結此印故</l><l>佛及善逝子</l>
<lb n="0207b26"/><l>諸大名稱者</l><l>妙觀察攝<note n="0207013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【明】</note><app n="0207013"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0207b27"/><l>憶昔本誓願</l><l>對於遍照尊</l>
<lb n="0207b28"/><l>不違教令故</l><l>加持使圓滿</l></lg>
<lb n="0207b29"/><p>次結一切諸佛如來<note n="0207014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安＋（樂）【甲】</note><app n="0207014"><lem>安</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">安樂</rdg></app>悅意歡喜三昧耶
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0207c" n="0207c"/>
<lb n="0207c01"/>印</p>
<lb n="0207c02"/><lg><l>十度堅固縛</l><l>忍願中交合</l>
<lb n="0207c03"/><l>檀慧與禪智</l><l>各相合而&CB00594;</l></lg>
<lb n="0207c04"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0207c05"/><p type="dharani">唵　三麼耶乎<note place="inline"><note n="0207015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207015"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app>引</note><note n="0207016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘇＋（上）夾註【乙】</note><app n="0207016"><lem>蘇</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">蘇<note place="inline">上</note></rdg></app>囉多薩怛梵<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0207c06"/><lg><l>由<note n="0207017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">示＝是【明】</note><app n="0207017"><lem>示</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>此印故</l><l>諸佛及菩薩</l>
<lb n="0207c07"/><l>一切執金剛</l><l>皆悉妙歡喜</l>
<lb n="0207c08"/><l>次當開心戶</l><l>入金剛智字</l>
<lb n="0207c09"/><l>觀於二乳上</l><l><note n="0207018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【明】</note><app n="0207018"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>怛囉<note n="0207019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＝右【明】</note><app n="0207019"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>吒</l>
<lb n="0207c10"/><l>如宮室戶扇</l><l>殊勝金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0207c11"/><l>三業同時發</l><l>拍心開兩字</l></lg>
<lb n="0207c12"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0207c13"/><p type="dharani">唵跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱<note place="inline"><note n="0207020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（聲）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207020"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">平聲</rdg></app></note>怛<note n="0207021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【明】【乙】</note><app n="0207021"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0207c14"/><lg><l>無始熏種子</l><l>所集之塵勞</l>
<lb n="0207c15"/><l>今以召罪印</l><l>集之欲摧碎</l>
<lb n="0207c16"/><l>十度堅固縛</l><l>忍願伸如針</l>
<lb n="0207c17"/><l>進力屈如鉤</l><l>心想召諸罪</l>
<lb n="0207c18"/><l>想彼眾罪狀</l><l><note n="0207022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">植＝直【明】</note><app n="0207022"><lem>植</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">直</rdg></app>髮裸黑形</l>
<lb n="0207c19"/><l><note n="0207023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及＝反【乙】</note><app n="0207023"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app>印刺於心</l><l>觸已誦密<note n="0207024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝言【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0207024"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0207c20"/><l>三業相應故</l><l>能召諸罪積</l>
<lb n="0207c21"/><l>誦此召集已</l><l>方作摧碎法</l></lg>
<lb n="0207c22"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0207c23"/><p type="dharani">唵薩婆播<note n="0207025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0207025"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>迦哩灑拏尾<note place="inline"><note n="0207026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0207026"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">入聲</rdg></app></note>輸馱<anchor id="fxT20p0207c01"/><note place="inline">入</note>娜三
<lb n="0207c24"/><note n="0207027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【乙】</note><app n="0207027"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>耶跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0207028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（薩怛&CB00085;二合）＋吽【乙】</note><app n="0207028"><lem>吽</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">薩怛&CB00085;二合吽</rdg></app>若<anchor id="fxT20p0207c02"/><note place="inline">入</note></p>
<lb n="0207c25"/><lg><l>召入於掌已</l><l>方作摧碎法</l>
<lb n="0207c26"/><l>前印內相叉</l><l>稱&CB00805;縛諸罪</l>
<lb n="0207c27"/><l>忍願俱伸直</l><l>有怛囉吒字</l>
<lb n="0207c28"/><l>想為金剛杵</l><l>相拍如摧山</l>
<lb n="0207c29"/><l>忿句及怒形</l><l>能淨諸惡趣</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0208a" n="0208a"/>
<lb n="0208a01"/><l>誦已忍願拍</l><l>三七隨所宜</l></lg>
<lb n="0208a02"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0208a03"/><p type="dharani">唵跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>播尼尾薩<note n="0208001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208001"><lem>普</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">普<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>吒也薩婆播也滿
<lb n="0208a04"/>馱娜&CB00135;&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>母乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>也薩婆播也<note n="0208002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00617;＝&CB00859;【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0208002"><lem>&CB00617;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00859;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0208a05"/>底<note n="0208003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔丁以反〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208003"><lem><note place="inline">丁以反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>避藥<note place="inline">二合重呼</note>薩婆薩怛<note n="0208004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挽＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208004"><lem>挽</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">挽<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>薩婆怛他<anchor id="fxT20p0208a01"/>&CB00617;
<lb n="0208a06"/>多跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>三<note n="0208005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0208005"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>也吽怛囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0208006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（短）【乙】</note><app n="0208006"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">合短</rdg></app></note>吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0208a07"/><lg><l><note n="0208007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以此＝此以【明】</note><app n="0208007"><lem>以此</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">此以</rdg></app>相應<note n="0208008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故＝門【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0208008"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">門</rdg></app></l><l>先佛方便說</l>
<lb n="0208a08"/><l>三業所積罪</l><l>無量極重障</l>
<lb n="0208a09"/><l>作此摧滅已</l><l>如火焚枯草</l>
<lb n="0208a10"/><l>有情常<note n="0208009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愚迷＝迷愚【明】</note><app n="0208009"><lem>愚迷</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">迷愚</rdg></app></l><l>不知此理趣</l>
<lb n="0208a11"/><l>如來大悲故</l><l>開此祕妙門</l>
<lb n="0208a12"/><l>次當結入印</l><l>內如來智字</l>
<lb n="0208a13"/><l>二羽堅固縛</l><l>禪智入於中</l>
<lb n="0208a14"/><l>以進力二度</l><l>相拄如環勢</l>
<lb n="0208a15"/><l>觀前八葉蓮</l><l>其上置阿字</l>
<lb n="0208a16"/><l>二點嚴飾故</l><l>妙字方名<note n="0208010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿＝惡【乙】</note><app n="0208010"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0208a17"/><l>色白如珂雪</l><l>流散千光明</l>
<lb n="0208a18"/><l>想以進力支</l><l>捻字安心內</l>
<lb n="0208a19"/><l>三業齊運用</l><l>誦此<note n="0208011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝真【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208011"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0208a20"/><p type="dharani">唵跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>味捨<note place="inline">平聲</note>惡<anchor id="fxT20p0208a02"/><note place="inline">入</note></p>
<lb n="0208a21"/><lg><l>既想入心中</l><l>字相逾光耀</l>
<lb n="0208a22"/><l>此即法界體</l><l>行者應是觀</l>
<lb n="0208a23"/><l>不久悟寂靜</l><l>法本不生故</l>
<lb n="0208a24"/><l>三世諸如來</l><l>金剛身口意</l>
<lb n="0208a25"/><l>皆以妙方便</l><l>持在金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0208a26"/><l>以此闔心門</l><l>智字獲堅固</l>
<lb n="0208a27"/><l>便屈進力度</l><l><note n="0208012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝拄【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208012"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">拄</rdg></app>於禪智背</l>
<lb n="0208a28"/><l>以印觸胸已</l><l>即誦此妙言</l></lg>
<lb n="0208a29"/><p type="dharani">唵跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>母瑟<note n="0208013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">致＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208013"><lem>致</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">致<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app><note n="0208014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00805;＋（平聲）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208014"><lem>&CB00805;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00805;<note place="inline">平聲</note></rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0208b" n="0208b"/>
<lb n="0208b01"/><lg><l>行者住等引</l><l>二羽堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0208b02"/><l>仰置於臍下</l><l>禪智蓮<note n="0208015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">花＝葉&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0208015"><lem>花</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">葉</rdg></app>形</l>
<lb n="0208b03"/><l>此名三昧印</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0208b04"/><p type="dharani">唵三摩地&CB00425;頭迷<note place="inline">二合</note>紇哩<note place="inline"><note n="0208016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">短＝二合【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208016"><lem>短</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">二合</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0208b05"/><lg><l>出息及入息</l><l>住阿那波那</l>
<lb n="0208b06"/><l>想佛遍虛空</l><l>彈指警覺我</l>
<lb n="0208b07"/><l>佛子汝云何</l><l>成無上等覺</l>
<lb n="0208b08"/><l>不知諸如來</l><l>實相之妙法</l>
<lb n="0208b09"/><l>既聞警覺已</l><l>行者復白言</l>
<lb n="0208b10"/><l>云何名真實</l><l>願最勝尊說</l>
<lb n="0208b11"/><l>諸佛皆歡喜</l><l>作如是勝言</l>
<lb n="0208b12"/><l>善哉摩訶薩</l><l>能作如是問</l>
<lb n="0208b13"/><l>汝想於心中</l><l>所內惡字門</l>
<lb n="0208b14"/><l>以字徹於心</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0208b15"/><p type="dharani">唵止<anchor id="fxT20p0208b01"/><note place="inline">入</note>多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline"><note n="0208017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0208017"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">平聲</rdg></app></note>味<note n="0208018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄧＋（去）夾註【乙】</note><app n="0208018"><lem>鄧</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">鄧<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app>迦路<note n="0208019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弭＋（平聲）細註【明】【乙】，（平）【甲】</note><app n="0208019"><lem>弭</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">弭<note place="inline">平聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">弭平</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0208b16"/><lg><l>當默誦一遍</l><l>便想為月輪</l>
<lb n="0208b17"/><l>倍欲精進故</l><l>復誦妙言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0208b18"/><p type="dharani">唵步提止<anchor id="fxT20p0208b02"/><note place="inline">入</note>多母<note place="inline"><note n="0208020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0208020"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>怛跛<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0208021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陀＝他【明】</note><app n="0208021"><lem>陀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">他</rdg></app>夜弭<anchor id="fxT20p0208b03"/><note place="inline">平</note></p>
<lb n="0208b19"/><lg><l>能令心月輪</l><l>圓滿甚清淨</l>
<lb n="0208b20"/><l>中想妙蓮花</l><l>上安寶金剛</l></lg>
<lb n="0208b21"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0208b22"/><p type="dharani">唵底瑟<note n="0208022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奼＝吒二合【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208022"><lem>奼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吒二合</rdg></app>麼尼<note place="inline"><note n="0208023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0208023"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0208b23"/><lg><l>引量同虛空</l><l>周遍於三界</l>
<lb n="0208b24"/><l>復誦此妙言</l><l>金剛語離聲</l></lg>
<lb n="0208b25"/><p type="dharani">唵薩頗<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0208b04"/>上</note>囉麼尼<anchor id="fxT20p0208b05"/><note place="inline">上</note>跋<note n="0208024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔日〕－【明】</note><app n="0208024"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼
<lb n="0208b26"/><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0208b27"/><lg><l>於此引妙蓮</l><l>流放千光焰</l>
<lb n="0208b28"/><l>一一光明中</l><l>無量佛剎土</l>
<lb n="0208b29"/><l>剎中有妙蓮</l><l>想持寶蓮者</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0208c" n="0208c"/>
<lb n="0208c01"/><l>持寶蓮勝幢</l><l>幢中出妙<note n="0208025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝音【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208025"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0208c02"/><l>誰有薄福者</l><l>當滿一切願</l>
<lb n="0208c03"/><l>住是寂三昧</l><l>為利諸有情</l>
<lb n="0208c04"/><l>如是菩薩類</l><l>皆住於等引</l>
<lb n="0208c05"/><l>從蓮花胎藏</l><l>放千妙光明</l>
<lb n="0208c06"/><l>皆為利眾生</l><l>檀波羅蜜等</l>
<lb n="0208c07"/><l>遍入諸三昧</l><l>理趣善巧門</l>
<lb n="0208c08"/><l>為愍念有情</l><l>作無量方便</l>
<lb n="0208c09"/><l>化身為種種</l><l>從生及涅槃</l>
<lb n="0208c10"/><l>轉大妙法輪</l><l>皆從意寶出</l>
<lb n="0208c11"/><l>所說之妙法</l><l>皆以輪成就</l>
<lb n="0208c12"/><l>以輪為妙智</l><l>能斷諸結使</l>
<lb n="0208c13"/><l>由轉<note n="0208026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙＝大【明】，大【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0208026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙＝大【明】，＝大【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0208026"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>法輪</l><l>此為福智路</l>
<lb n="0208c14"/><l>次皆正觀察</l><l>漸斂其智蓮</l></lg>
<lb n="0208c15"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0208c16"/><p type="dharani">唵僧訶囉麼尼跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0208027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0208027"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0208c17"/><lg><l>所在諸如來</l><l>皆入為一體</l>
<lb n="0208c18"/><l>猶如於明鏡</l><l>能現於萬像</l>
<lb n="0208c19"/><l>法界自性體</l><l>住於金剛蓮</l>
<lb n="0208c20"/><l>即變其寶蓮</l><l>為真多菩薩</l>
<lb n="0208c21"/><l>手持如意寶</l><l>六臂身金色</l>
<lb n="0208c22"/><l>皆想於自身</l><l>頂髻寶莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0208c23"/><l><note n="0208028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冠＝別【甲】</note><app n="0208028"><lem>冠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">別</rdg></app>坐自在王</l><l>住於說法相</l>
<lb n="0208c24"/><l>第一手思惟</l><l>愍念有情故</l>
<lb n="0208c25"/><l>第二持意寶</l><l>能滿一切願</l>
<lb n="0208c26"/><l>第三持念珠</l><l>為度傍生苦</l>
<lb n="0208c27"/><l>左按光明山</l><l>成就無傾動</l>
<lb n="0208c28"/><l>第二持蓮手</l><l>能淨諸非法</l>
<lb n="0208c29"/><l>第三<note n="0208029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挈＝契&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0208029"><lem>挈</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">契</rdg></app>輪手</l><l>能轉無上法</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0209a" n="0209a"/>
<lb n="0209a01"/><l>六臂廣<note n="0209001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">博＝幡【甲】</note><app n="0209001"><lem>博</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">幡</rdg></app>體</l><l>能遊於六道</l>
<lb n="0209a02"/><l>以大悲方便</l><l>斷諸有情苦</l>
<lb n="0209a03"/><l>行者如是觀</l><l>坐於月輪中</l>
<lb n="0209a04"/><l>身流千光明</l><l>項背皆圓光</l>
<lb n="0209a05"/><l>復想心月輪</l><l>亦有寶蓮花</l>
<lb n="0209a06"/><l>以是能堅固</l><l>無動觀已身</l>
<lb n="0209a07"/><l>為離諸妄想</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0209a08"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00135;哩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0209002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0209002"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT20p0209a01"/><note place="inline">去</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛<note n="0209003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＋（二合）夾註【乙】</note><app n="0209003"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">娜<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>跋日
<lb n="0209a09"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句唅三<note n="0209004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0209004"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>喻唅
<lb n="0209a10"/><anchor id="fxT20p0209a02"/>摩訶三<anchor id="fxT20p0209a03"/>摩喻唅薩婆怛他<anchor id="fxT20p0209a04"/>孽<note n="0209005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＋（引）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0209005"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">多<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>避三菩地
<lb n="0209a11"/>囉怛<note n="0209006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0209006"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">娜<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句
<lb n="0209a12"/>唅</p>
<lb n="0209a13"/><lg><l>以此法<note n="0209007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝加【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0209007"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">加</rdg></app>持</l><l>十度芙蓉合</l>
<lb n="0209a14"/><l>進力屈如寶</l><l>印心額喉頂</l>
<lb n="0209a15"/><l>吽字想於心</l><l>怛囉安於額</l>
<lb n="0209a16"/><l>訖哩當喉上</l><l>惡字置於頂</l>
