<lb n="0210a11"/>麼訶三麼也薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0210a12"/><lg><l>次以內外供</l><l>供養蓮花王</l>
<lb n="0210a13"/><l>所謂內供養</l><l>芙蓉掌當心</l>
<lb n="0210a14"/><l>禪智並伸直</l><l>名為蓮花喜</l>
<lb n="0210a15"/><l>應誦此密言</l></lg>
<lb n="0210a16"/><p type="dharani">唵摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>那&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉細<note place="inline">引</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0210a17"/><lg><l>次結花鬘印</l><l>以此而供養</l>
<lb n="0210a18"/><l>不易前喜印</l><l>二手捧向前</l>
<lb n="0210a19"/><l>想種種寶鬘</l><l>遍滿虛空界</l></lg>
<lb n="0210a20"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210a21"/><p type="dharani">唵摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>娜&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>麼&CB00619;吽</p>
<lb n="0210a22"/><lg><l>次應<note n="0210006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝此【甲】</note><app n="0210006"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>歌印</l><l>奉獻智蓮者</l>
<lb n="0210a23"/><l>復以前妙印</l><l>屈掌<note n="0210007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挂＝拄【乙】</note><app n="0210007"><lem>挂</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">拄</rdg></app>諸度</l>
<lb n="0210a24"/><l>從臍漸至口</l><l>散下如寫勢</l>
<lb n="0210a25"/><l>想緊那羅音</l><l>供養諸聖者</l></lg>
<lb n="0210a26"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210a27"/><p type="dharani">唵摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>那&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>儗<note place="inline">研以反</note>帝<note place="inline">平</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0210a28"/><lg><l>次應結舞印</l><l>前印左右旋</l>
<lb n="0210a29"/><l>合芙蓉妙掌</l><l>安於頂上散</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0210b" n="0210b"/>
<lb n="0210b01"/><l>由是四供養</l><l>能獲大神通</l></lg>
<lb n="0210b02"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210b03"/><p type="dharani">唵摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>娜&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;俚<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">平</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0210b04"/><lg><l>作此四供養</l><l>能成最勝事</l>
<lb n="0210b05"/><l><note n="0210008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＝他【甲】</note><app n="0210008"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">他</rdg></app>結外供養</l><l>喜心而獻之</l>
<lb n="0210b06"/><l>運心無邊界</l><l>蓮花焚香法</l>
<lb n="0210b07"/><l>諸佛誠言說</l><l>為利諸有情</l>
<lb n="0210b08"/><l>蓮掌向下散</l><l>猶如焚香勢</l>
<lb n="0210b09"/><l>誦此祕密言</l><l>想<note n="0210009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香雲供養＝供養香雲【乙】</note><app n="0210009"><lem>香雲供養</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">供養香雲</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0210b10"/><l>周遍虛空界</l><l>供養諸聖眾</l></lg>
<lb n="0210b11"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>娜度閉<note place="inline">平</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0210b12"/><lg><l>次應結花印</l><l>以三十二相</l>
<lb n="0210b13"/><l>莊嚴諸如來</l><l>觀妙色花雲</l>
<lb n="0210b14"/><l>運心遍一切</l><l>如前合蓮掌</l>
<lb n="0210b15"/><l>上散如花勢</l><l>供養諸如來</l>
<lb n="0210b16"/><l>及諸善逝子</l><l>想滿虛空界</l>
<lb n="0210b17"/><l>花雲妙芬馥</l><l>寶樹極端嚴</l>
<lb n="0210b18"/><l>誦此祕密語</l><l>三業齊運用</l></lg>
<lb n="0210b19"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>娜補瑟閉<anchor id="fxT20p0210b01"/><note place="inline">平</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0210b20"/><lg><l>眾生無明覆</l><l>離於智慧光</l>
<lb n="0210b21"/><l>為彼淨除故</l><l>應結智燈印</l>
<lb n="0210b22"/><l>以前蓮花掌</l><l>禪智&CB00594;相逼</l>
<lb n="0210b23"/><l>心想<note n="0210010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210010"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>尼燈</l><l>遍照虛空界</l>
<lb n="0210b24"/><l>所出無量光</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0210b25"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>那&CB00135;<note place="inline">&CB00135;熠<note n="0210011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0210011"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note><note n="0210012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閉＋（平聲）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210012"><lem>閉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">閉<note place="inline">平聲</note></rdg></app>吽</p>
<lb n="0210b26"/><lg><l>智者次應結</l><l>解脫塗香印</l>
<lb n="0210b27"/><l>為淨眾生故</l><l>獻此尸羅香</l>
<lb n="0210b28"/><l>二手散蓮掌</l><l>當心塗香勢</l>
<lb n="0210b29"/><l>十度成熏習</l><l>香海遍虛空</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0210c" n="0210c"/>
<lb n="0210c01"/><l>獻佛及所尊</l><l>誦此祕密語</l></lg>
<lb n="0210c02"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>摯拏<note place="inline">二合</note>娜巘提吽</p>
<lb n="0210c03"/><lg><l>內外供養已</l><l>然後應順念</l>
<lb n="0210c04"/><l>結祕<note n="0210013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝根【乙】</note><app n="0210013"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">根</rdg></app>本印</l><l>以對密言王</l>
<lb n="0210c05"/><l>先誦根本言</l><l>分明七遍已</l>
<lb n="0210c06"/><l>平掌當於心</l><l>忍願如蓮花</l>
<lb n="0210c07"/><l>進力摩尼狀</l><l>餘度盡如幢</l>
<lb n="0210c08"/><l>誦根本密言</l><l>思滿有情願</l></lg>
<lb n="0210c09"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210c10"/><p type="dharani">娜麼囉怛娜怛囉夜也那莫阿唎耶&CB00085;嚕吉帝
<lb n="0210c11"/>濕伐囉耶菩地薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>耶麼訶薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0210c12"/>耶麼訶迦嚕尼迦耶怛姪<note place="inline">&CB00135;也<anchor id="fxT20p0210c01"/>反</note>他唵斫迦囉靺
<lb n="0210c13"/>低真多末尼麼訶&CB00425;娜迷嚕嚕底<note place="inline">丁以<anchor id="fxT20p0210c02"/>反</note>瑟<note n="0210014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00109;＝吒【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210014"><lem>&CB00109;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0210c14"/><note place="inline">二合</note>入<note n="0210015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0210015"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>&CB00256;阿迦哩灑<note place="inline">二合</note>耶吽<note n="0210016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發＝癹【明】，泮【甲】</note><note n="0210016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">發＝癹【明】，＝泮【甲】</note><app n="0210016"><lem>發</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">癹</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">泮</rdg></app>吒薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0210c15"/><note n="0210017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210017"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">合<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></note><note n="0210018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210018"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0210c16"/><lg><l>次結心祕密</l><l>依前根本印</l>
<lb n="0210c17"/><l>戒方檀慧<note n="0210019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【明】</note><app n="0210019"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app></l><l>名為本心印</l>
<lb n="0210c18"/><l>一切諸意願</l><l>應心之所念</l>
<lb n="0210c19"/><l>由結此印故</l><l>皆悉得成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0210c20"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210c21"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;那<note n="0210020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210020"><lem>迷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">迷<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>真多麼抳入<anchor id="fxT20p0210c03"/>&CB00085;&CB00256;吽</p>
<lb n="0210c22"/><lg><l>次結隨心印</l><l>二手堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0210c23"/><l>進力<note n="0210021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】【乙】</note><app n="0210021"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>尼形</l><l>禪智並而申</l>
<lb n="0210c24"/><l>戒<note n="0210022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＝法【明】</note><app n="0210022"><lem>方</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>亦舒直</l><l>檀慧相交&CB00594;</l>
<lb n="0210c25"/><l>誦此心中心</l></lg>
<lb n="0210c26"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0210c27"/><p type="dharani">唵末囉娜&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0210c04"/>迷吽</p>
<lb n="0210c28"/><lg><l>次想尊口中</l><l>流出祕密言</l>
<lb n="0210c29"/><l>分明成字道</l><l>五色光照耀</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0211a" n="0211a"/>
<lb n="0211a01"/><l>間錯殊勝色</l><l>入於瑜岐口</l>
<lb n="0211a02"/><l>列心月輪中</l><l>瑩如紅<note n="0211001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頗黎＝玻&CB00226;【明】【乙】</note><app n="0211001"><lem>頗黎</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">玻&CB00226;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0211a03"/><l>一一諦思惟</l><l>順理隨覺悟</l>
<lb n="0211a04"/><l>住定而修習</l><l>入於阿字門</l>
<lb n="0211a05"/><l>即入輪字觀</l><l>皆遍觀諸字</l>
<lb n="0211a06"/><l>此名三昧念</l><l>獲智及解脫</l>
<lb n="0211a07"/><l>由此相應故</l><l>不久成種智</l>
<lb n="0211a08"/><l>若<note n="0211002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0211002"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>聲順念</l><l>最勝妙奇特</l>
<lb n="0211a09"/><l>住於本尊觀</l><l>不應急躁心</l>
<lb n="0211a10"/><l>不高亦不下</l><l>不緩亦不急</l>
<lb n="0211a11"/><l>智者離分別</l><l>及諸妄想心</l>
<lb n="0211a12"/><l>若誦洛叉遍</l><l>所求皆悉地</l>
<lb n="0211a13"/><l>二手持念珠</l><l>頗胝與蓮<note n="0211003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝字【明】</note><app n="0211003"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">字</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0211a14"/><l>螺珠及餘寶</l><l>無瑕光好者</l>
<lb n="0211a15"/><l>當穿一百八</l><l>一一誦七遍</l>
<lb n="0211a16"/><l>心及心中心</l><l>或毘俱多羅</l>
<lb n="0211a17"/><l>作此法加持</l><l>穿貫珠鬘已</l>
<lb n="0211a18"/><l>當心一一度</l><l>與莎訶齊聲</l>
<lb n="0211a19"/><l>一千與百八</l><l>隨力而念誦</l>
<lb n="0211a20"/><l>四時或三時</l><l>此法後夜勝</l>
<lb n="0211a21"/><l>如意輪經中</l><l>本教佛所說</l>
<lb n="0211a22"/><l>若如是修習</l><l>現世證初地</l>
<lb n="0211a23"/><l>過此十六生</l><l>成無上菩提</l>
<lb n="0211a24"/><l>何況世悉地</l><l>現生不如意</l>
<lb n="0211a25"/><l>隨力念誦已</l><l>重結三昧耶</l>
<lb n="0211a26"/><l>復為八供養</l><l>發遣密言主</l>
<lb n="0211a27"/><l>二羽堅固縛</l><l>忍願蓮<note n="0211004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">葉＝華【明】【乙】</note><app n="0211004"><lem>葉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">華</rdg></app>形</l>
<lb n="0211a28"/><l>從心至面散</l><l>頂上合花掌</l>
<lb n="0211a29"/><l>想尊虛空中</l><l>復道還宮去</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1086.0211b" n="0211b"/>
<lb n="0211b01"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0211b02"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>紇<note n="0211005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哩＋（二合）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0211005"><lem>哩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">哩<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>穆</p>
<lb n="0211b03"/><lg><l>發遣聖者已</l><l>自住本尊觀</l>
<lb n="0211b04"/><l>或於閑靜處</l><l>轉讀摩訶衍</l>
<lb n="0211b05"/><l>楞伽與花嚴</l><l>般若及理趣</l>
<lb n="0211b06"/><l>如是等經教</l><l>思惟而修習</l>
<lb n="0211b07"/><l><note n="0211006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦讀＝讀誦【明】【乙】</note><app n="0211006"><lem>誦讀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">讀誦</rdg></app>經典已</l><l>自恣行住坐</l>
<lb n="0211b08"/><l>乃至於寢息</l><l>不間菩提心</l>
<lb n="0211b09"/><l>不久當悉地</l><l>金剛藏所說</l>
<lb n="0211b10"/><l>此大悲軌儀</l><l>不擇日及宿</l>
<lb n="0211b11"/><l>時食與澡浴</l><l>若淨與不淨</l>
<lb n="0211b12"/><l>常應不間斷</l><l>遠離於散亂</l>
<lb n="0211b13"/><l>空閑寂靜處</l><l>不營諸世務</l>
<lb n="0211b14"/><l>念畢發誓願</l><l>結三昧耶印</l>
<lb n="0211b15"/><l>禮佛菩薩已</l><l>隨意而經行</l></lg>
<lb n="0211b16"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>觀自在菩薩如意輪瑜伽<note n="0211007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一卷＝念誦法【明】【乙】</note><app n="0211007"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">念誦法</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
